.sh NAME
abort  \*-  generate an IOT fault
.sh SYNOPSIS
.bd abort()
.sh DESCRIPTION
.it Abort
executes the IOT instruction.
This is usually considered a program
fault by the system and results in
termination with a core dump.
It is used to generate a core image
for debugging.
